23#ifndef UCHAR_MAX
24#define UCHAR_MAX 255
25#endif
26
27enum cmap_builtin { CMAP_BUILTIN };
28
29class cmap {
30public:
31 cmap();
32 cmap(cmap_builtin);
33 int operator()(unsigned char) const;
34 unsigned char &operator[](unsigned char);
35
36 friend class cmap_init;
37private:
38 unsigned char v[UCHAR_MAX+1];
39};
40
41inline int cmap::operator()(unsigned char c) const
42{
43 return v[c];
44}
45
46inline unsigned char &cmap::operator[](unsigned char c)
47{
48 return v[c];
49}
50
51extern cmap cmlower;
52extern cmap cmupper;
53
54static class cmap_init {
55 static int initialised;
56public:
57 cmap_init();
58} _cmap_init;
